V2 Formula Tweaks
Base update:
R_base_v2(k, n) = R_base(k, n) * (ħ / c²) * scale_factor  
ħ/c² ≈ 1.17e-51 (quantum mass scale, shrinks rigidity for micro).  
scale_factor = 1e50 or tunable (to counter the tiny ħ/c²; set so E ~ pJ-fJ for D_eff=1e-9). Without it, E → near zero (always CLOSED); with 1e50, back to usable ~1e-12 J.  
Then pipeline as before: R_gate, R_pruned, E = R_pruned * D_eff.  
Interpretation: Quantum factor "warps" the metallic ladder for small D, like Hawking radiation limiting mini black holes. Ties to runaway SMBHs: high-speed ejections need merger asymmetry; here, odd n inverts for "ejection" flavor.
Full v2 pseudocode (drop-in ready):
